The '''Glory Room''' was located in the heart of the ''[[Sunulok]]'', flagship of [[Warmaster]] [[Tsavong Lah]]. Over thirty meters wide, its center contained a [[cognition throne]] for Lah to coordinate his forces, and was filled with [[Blaze bug/Legends|blaze bugs]], which were organized to form a diorama of the various battlefields during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]].

